00:00:08.469 --> 00:00:10.889
Today we will make paneer kheer.

00:00:11.091 --> 00:00:16.099
Paneer kheer is very delicious and can be cooked instantly.

00:00:16.548 --> 00:00:23.583
It can be prepared for any party or any special occasion.

00:00:23.793 --> 00:00:29.333
Let’s see what all ingredients are required for making paneer kheer.

00:00:29.769 --> 00:00:32.134
Paneer - 250 grams

00:00:32.661 --> 00:00:35.717
Sugar - 100 grams (1/2 cup)

00:00:36.155 --> 00:00:39.854
Cardamom powder - ½ tsp

00:00:40.216 --> 00:00:42.319
Cashew nuts - 6-7

00:00:43.171 --> 00:00:45.972
Milk - ½ liter (full cream)

00:00:47.057 --> 00:00:51.969
For making kheer firstly boil milk.

00:00:52.339 --> 00:00:53.395
Turn on the gas.

00:00:57.235 --> 00:01:02.885
Meanwhile grate paneer.

00:01:15.484 --> 00:01:20.261
When milk starts boiling add paneer into it.

00:01:41.043 --> 00:01:47.238
After adding paneer cook milk until it starts boiling again.

00:01:47.709 --> 00:01:56.682
Cook on medium flame and stir after every 2-3 minutes.

00:01:57.193 --> 00:01:59.582
Simmer until it gets thick in consistency.

00:02:04.716 --> 00:02:07.875
Meanwhile cut cashew nuts as well.

00:02:15.618 --> 00:02:25.195
Kheer has become thick now add sugar into it as per your taste.

00:02:26.534 --> 00:02:30.185
Also add cashew nuts and cardamom powder.

00:02:36.386 --> 00:02:40.513
Cook for 1-2 minutes more until sugar gets dissolved.

00:02:43.299 --> 00:02:46.346
Kheer is ready; turn off the gas.

00:02:46.688 --> 00:02:48.617
Take out kheer in a serving bowl.

00:03:00.656 --> 00:03:05.640
Garnish with chopped pistachios.

00:03:11.527 --> 00:03:14.154
Very tempting and appetizing kheer is ready.

00:03:14.211 --> 00:03:16.981
It is also known as chena kheer.

00:03:17.255 --> 00:03:26.641
Serve piping hot or store in refrigerator and then serve. It tastes more awesome.

00:03:27.298 --> 00:03:31.893
Paneer kheer can be stored in refrigerator for 2-3 days.

